          <title>PwC Study Reveals Investors' Optimism on Global Economic Growth and AI Adoption</title>
          <description><![CDATA[A recent PwC study reveals that investors are optimistic about global economic growth, with 53% anticipating an increase in the next 12 months. The study also finds that three-quarters of investors believe generative AI tools will boost productivity and drive business growth.]]></description>
